strategy: I decided to try fusing 3 times and then extract the max points.
use up to five button presses to combine crystals then use the other 5 to extract

It was always best to fuse first. This was because multiplication increases far more rapidly than addition when summing them at the end. If a fuse failed however it was best to then stop as significant progress is lost in  trying to generate a greater number. Too much fuse however started to also lose value so it was best to pay attention to the numbers and also how many attempts were left as the ideal best value was somewhere in the middle.
